        "meta_text": "DERMATOLOGIST INSIGHTS",
        "headline": "5 Things Dermatologists Wish You Knew About Foundation After 40",
        "intro_text": "Board-certified dermatologists see the same foundation mistakes every week in their clinics. Here's what they want you to know — and what they tell their own patients to do differently.",
        "image_asset": "lp-derm-foundation-hero.jpg",
        "image_alt": "Woman with radiant, healthy-looking skin",
        "caption": "What dermatologists actually recommend may surprise you.",
        "bg_color": "#ffffff",
