    "rich_text_problems_012": {
      "type": "vl-rich-text",
      "settings": {
        "subheading": "If This Sounds Familiar...",
        "content": "<p>You've spent years dealing with foundations that don't work the way they should:</p><ul><li>A shade that looked perfect in-store but completely wrong at home</li><li>Coverage that settles into fine lines and pores by noon</li><li>Foundation that oxidises and turns orange within hours</li><li>Skin that feels drier at the end of the day than when you started</li><li>Products that promise \"anti-aging\" but deliver nothing measurable</li><li>The nagging feeling that every foundation is made for someone 20 years younger</li></ul><p>You're not imagining it. And it's not your skin's fault.</p>",
        "bg_color": "#faf9f7",
        "heading_color": "#000000",
        "text_color": "#333333",
        "link_color": "#5C1A33"
      }
    },
    "image_text_product_013": {
      "type": "vl-image-text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/freepik__add-the-two-products-together-into-a-studiostyle-p__90794.png",
        "image_alt": "Vera Lane Tone Adapting Foundation",
        "image_caption": "One formula. Your unique shade. Every time.",
        "heading": "Meet the Tone Adapting Foundation",
        "text": "<p>Everything the dermatologists above recommend — in a single formula. Tone-adapting pigments that match your unique skin chemistry in 60 seconds. Hyaluronic acid and glycerin for clinical-grade hydration. Vitamin E for antioxidant protection. Bisabolol to soothe reactive skin.</p><p>Fragrance-free. Dermatologist-tested. No parabens, sulfates, or drying alcohols. A foundation built around what your skin actually needs after 40 — not what a marketing team thinks you'll pay for.</p>",
        "bg_color": "#ffffff",
        "heading_color": "#000000",
        "text_color": "#333333"
      }
